WEBVTT

00:11:29.727 --> 00:11:33.851
which is rational
and well-informed citizens.

00:11:34.605 --> 00:11:37.136
Muslims are like canaries
in the coal mine.

00:11:37.655 --> 00:11:39.346
We might be the first to feel it,

00:11:39.370 --> 00:11:43.407
but the toxic air of fear
is harming us all.

00:11:44.251 --> 00:11:49.804
(Applause)

00:11:51.580 --> 00:11:53.979
And assigning collective guilt

00:11:54.003 --> 00:11:56.841
isn't just about having
to explain yourself all the time.

00:11:57.777 --> 00:12:01.425
